a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1661%2c20221031%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,1661,20221031,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1661","JDATE":"20221031","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}